reviewText: My son just recently started watching bananas in pajamas and he gets a kick out of it :) love the availability to find it on here and on VHS! Awesome!
The cutest duo in the history of motion picture! Grew up watching this and I'm very happy that my kids were able to experience that feeling too!
Cute wholesome video - part of Bananas Pajamas series.  My 6 yr. old twin grandsons love it.
